{"id": 2680, "genre": 1001, "title": "日常生活中，你都听过哪些适得其反的“安慰”？", "description": "欢迎欣赏《无效安慰大全》100 句。（题图来自：iStock ©️ CSA-Printstock）", "record_count": 3508, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20181217174205hOLZcsy6mHe8tvjN.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-12-18T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 317184, "content": "开心点儿", "image": null, "praise_count": 57, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1515874}, {"id": 320768, "content": "你读书读傻了...", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1206725}, {"id": 317185, "content": "我怕自己哪天死到地里了，也看不到你们结婚", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1534540}, {"id": 317186, "content": "没关系，下次继续努力就好", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1532264}, {"id": 317698, "content": "至于么", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1434914}, {"id": 317954, "content": "其实我也考的不好", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1537253}, {"id": 317187, "content": "所以怎么安慰人，我一直不太会…", "image": null, "praise_count": 33, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 356641}, {"id": 317188, "content": "你不会的，别人也不会。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1334527}, {"id": 317189, "content": "喝两口根本吹不出来。～酒驾", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 838601}, {"id": 317190, "content": "从没受过伤型", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1066507}, {"id": 317191, "content": "正常~\n你不懂~\n还是你见得太少了~", "image": null, "praise_count": 39, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 147875}, {"id": 317192, "content": "现在苦一点，以后回过头来看看呢？", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1403041}, {"id": 317193, "content": "这里面提及的安慰大多对我有效", "image": null, "praise_count": 48, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 771841}, {"id": 317194, "content": "多喝热水", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1435621}, {"id": 318474, "content": "尽人事，听天命。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1540056}, {"id": 323594, "content": "不要哭", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1563559}, {"id": 317195, "content": "多大点事嘛", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1526189}, {"id": 317963, "content": "没什么的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1303803}, {"id": 318475, "content": "大家都可以做到，为什么到你这儿就不行了？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1540056}, {"id": 317196, "content": "第一个居然那么多认同……会这么说，不是因为早就提醒还不注意，结果害到别人帮忙收拾烂摊子或是来吐苦水", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1085613}, {"id": 317452, "content": "你不胖。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1530150}, {"id": 326668, "content": "要开心", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1578458}, {"id": 317197, "content": "我劝你善良", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1446784}, {"id": 317198, "content": "就当花钱买了教训！", "image": null, "praise_count": 43, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1038659}, {"id": 317199, "content": "不是啥大事儿别麻烦了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1534988}, {"id": 317200, "content": "舍财免灾！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1038659}, {"id": 317201, "content": "尽力就好了…", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1534989}, {"id": 317202, "content": "别人都好好的，为什么偏偏到你这儿就出错了呢？\n别人没挨打，为什么就你挨打了呢？\n那么多人不针对，为什么偏要针对你呢？\n那么多人不骂，为什么偏要骂你呢？\n……", "image": null, "praise_count": 55, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1068079}, {"id": 317203, "content": "喝点热水就好了", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1429530}, {"id": 317459, "content": "在吗？在干嘛？吃了吗？睡了吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1532902}, {"id": 317204, "content": "哎呀，我见过比你这更**的，你这算啥。", "image": null, "praise_count": 33, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1534996}, {"id": 317972, "content": "所以我受过的安慰都是适得其反的😰", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1528870}, {"id": 317206, "content": "刚出来工作，遇到这种事是正常的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1444965}, {"id": 317207, "content": "胖点好，有安全感", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 144513}, {"id": 317208, "content": "不管什么事情都让你看开点，想开点，", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1315070}, {"id": 317209, "content": "我就过来看看评论学习学习", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1531372}, {"id": 317210, "content": "是挺扎心的，没事没事，下次再来。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1518271}, {"id": 317722, "content": "赞同前面网友所说的，再来一个“如何有效安慰”调查，再结合这个“无效安慰”一起服用岂不是更佳？🌝🌝", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1413882}, {"id": 318490, "content": "哈哈哈哈shabi", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1539711}, {"id": 317211, "content": "怎么就你有问题 别人怎么没问题", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1534906}, {"id": 317212, "content": "其实 还好吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1413059}, {"id": 317213, "content": "就不要说无效的安慰了吧，说点有效的，真的不知道怎么安慰别人，都看起来太无力了", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1274904}, {"id": 317214, "content": "也让你体会一下，我们有多不容易", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1529652}, {"id": 317726, "content": "没事啦这点小事", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1536737}, {"id": 319518, "content": "别着急，着急也没用", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1459976}, {"id": 317215, "content": "没关系……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1522827}, {"id": 317216, "content": "做人呢，最重要的就是开心，你饿不饿啊，煮碗面给你吃···", "image": "img/option/option/20181218133444mDEl8UwZc1pqMFsu.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1349071}, {"id": 317217, "content": "都会过去的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1531597}, {"id": 317218, "content": "我知道，我明白，我懂，然后开始巴拉巴拉跟安慰无关的个人价值观~", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1146993}, {"id": 317219, "content": "其实你什么都不要做，给我个拥抱，认认真真听我说说话，陪我喝酒，然后确认我安全到家睡觉，就是最好的安慰~", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1146993}]}